TITLE: Creating and using a Pinia instance in a Vue.js application
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to create a Pinia instance and add it to a Vue.js application as a plugin. It includes importing necessary functions, creating the Pinia instance, and using it in the app.
SOURCE: https://github.com/vuejs/pinia/blob/v3/packages/docs/getting-started.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: js
CODE:
```
import { createApp } from 'vue'
import { createPinia } from 'pinia'
import App from './App.vue'

const pinia = createPinia()
const app = createApp(App)

app.use(pinia)
app.mount('#app')
