TITLE: Using Pinia Store in Components
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use a Pinia store within a Vue component using the composition API. Shows store initialization and property extraction using storeToRefs.
SOURCE: https://github.com/vuejs/pinia/blob/v3/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { useMainStore } from '@/stores/main'
import { storeToRefs } from 'pinia'

export default defineComponent({
  setup() {
    const main = useMainStore()

    const { counter, doubleCounter } = storeToRefs(main)

    return {
      main,
      counter,
      doubleCounter,
    }
  },
})
```

