TITLE: Setup Store Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to create a Pinia store using the Composition API setup style with refs, computed properties, and functions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/vuejs/pinia/blob/v3/packages/docs/core-concepts/index.md#2025-04-22_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
export const useCounterStore = defineStore('counter', () => {
  const count = ref(0)
  const name = ref('Eduardo')
  const doubleCount = computed(() => count.value * 2)
  function increment() {
    count.value++
  }

  return { count, name, doubleCount, increment }
})
```

