TITLE: Implementing a Debounce Plugin for Pinia
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to create a Pinia plugin that reads custom options and wraps actions with debounce functionality using lodash.
SOURCE: https://github.com/vuejs/pinia/blob/v3/packages/docs/core-concepts/plugins.md#2025-04-22_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
// use any debounce library
import debounce from 'lodash/debounce'

pinia.use(({ options, store }) => {
  if (options.debounce) {
    // we are overriding the actions with new ones
    return Object.keys(options.debounce).reduce((debouncedActions, action) => {
      debouncedActions[action] = debounce(
        store[action],
        options.debounce[action]
      )
      return debouncedActions
    }, {})
  }
})
```

