TITLE: Unit Testing Vue Components with Pinia Stores in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to set up and perform unit tests for Vue components that use Pinia stores, including mocking store actions and manipulating state.
SOURCE: https://github.com/vuejs/pinia/blob/v3/packages/docs/cookbook/testing.md#2025-04-22_snippet_3

