TITLE: Demonstrating Store Composition Rules in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet illustrates the rules for composing stores in Pinia, showing both incorrect and correct ways to use stores within each other. It emphasizes that direct state reading between stores in setup functions can lead to infinite loops.
